reviews.review_text: Carolina blue I remember what a great venue and setting Chapel Hill was. Beautiful blue skies and the security force was comprised of students in blue Dean Dome jackets. No alcohol either. Somehow the great attitude of the town balanced just right. Balloons everywhere. Juxtaposed against Atlanta there was just no comparison in energy and enjoyment potential. Why do i say these things? Objectively speaking, these were some of the sweetest shows i had ever seen.Spanish Jam! Rolling sweet thunder on the GDTRFB. Got my first MD the next night.Nuff said. Nice work on the recording sir. Thank you.
